*gcc-config-1.3.8-r1 (24 Dec 2004)

  24 Dec 2004; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> files/gcc-config-1.3.8,
  +gcc-config-1.3.8-r1.ebuild, -gcc-config-1.3.8.ebuild:
